[It is reassuring to learn that although this case of measles was detected in initially by an airport thermal body scanner, there appears to have been no onward transmission of the virus infection either to passengers and crew, or to airport ground staff. A map of Taiwan can be accessed at: http://www.mapsofworld.com/taiwan/taiwan-political-map.htm. - Mod.CP]
